{"tid":88500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「巨乳教師」找13歲學生做愛懷孕　無恥喊：他家人很開心！","createTime":"2017-01-20T16:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T13:20:48.000Z","uid":78001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"580be73706dfaacf882793d5ff7ffa8a59cad787","tid":88500,"uid":78001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"▲薇拉找13歲男學生天天做愛，甚至還懷孕。（圖／翻攝自Alexandria Vera臉書下同）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQYiM6yVc4HbHoKjh39PuNmZGxuYKrQvc6PmvZqMfFzH4?filename=40q037e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40q037e.jpg&h=26a72e20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/000251_613fafe0bf2fb85fcd1c5630595ebfb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F000251_613fafe0bf2fb85fcd1c5630595ebfb7.jpg&h=95a39144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為人師表還是「為人師婊」？美國德州24歲英文老師薇拉(Alexandria Vera)被爆出和中學學生公然在課堂上打情罵俏，甚至在去年懷了13歲男學生的小孩，在開庭時還大言不慚表示：「學生家長知道我懷孕的事情都非常開心好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n根據英國每日郵報報導，薇拉自2015年夏天遇到當時就讀8年級（13歲）的男學生，因為她身材火辣馬上就讓情竇初開的學生心動，之後兩人展開驚天動地的熱戀，幾乎天天做愛。有同班同學出面指證，該名男同學和薇拉完全不避諱的在同學們面前秀恩愛，甚至男方還會當眾捏老師屁股，畫面充滿情色挑逗。<br />\n<br />\n薇拉不久後懷孕，案情曝光後更向法官供稱，「男同學家長都很歡迎我到他們家過夜做愛，對於懷孕這件事情更是開心表示祝福。」但檢察官資料則顯示，薇拉刻意找了男學生跟男學生的爸爸到家裡，來掩飾歪斜的師生關系。<br />\n<br />\n而薇拉遭捕後的精神治療師則表示，薇拉因為從小目睹過家庭暴力，所以強烈需要愛及關註，她可能真的愛上的那個孩子，但忘了這件事是錯的。此外，檢察官在薇拉手機中發現與男學生拍的色情照片，並曾傳過邀約做愛的訊息。法官認為，「由於薇拉並非強迫與男同學發生性行為，從原本的求處30年徒刑降為10年徒刑。」"},{"pid":"76b53cc65cb5cc98f8027d03a895ef7d94ecb459","tid":88500,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"快點每日找我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687955946380dd21e4cf2bb81afd60e3195db392","tid":88500,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"放開個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有本事黎攪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ddd428bc8d349fee80f67516f28ac25a79b950","tid":88500,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"快啲搵我"},{"pid":"2a3d78bf2ded5af38cdf18a9251553edf76f6400","tid":88500,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"真是美女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c4dd75e02ef646e8b96db180d65b9f99af1fc0","tid":88500,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"呢次真係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184620149f30a6d8340fce16b0620e5050244f75","tid":88500,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"又如搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60baae1ea71719c4ae69dc73edf2972886207bfb","tid":88500,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"今次我要啦"},{"pid":"aa46efffa10db9fe341705b7190b1b61d63da14c","tid":88500,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.click2houston.com/photo/2016/06/01/Alexandria%20Vera%20mug_1464797852368_6604409_ver1.0_640_360.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.click2houston.com%2Fphoto%2F2016%2F06%2F01%2FAlexandria%2520Vera%2520mug_1464797852368_6604409_ver1.0_640_360.JPG&h=0714b70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.hdnux.com/photos/51/62/61/10955855/3/1024x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.hdnux.com%2Fphotos%2F51%2F62%2F61%2F10955855%2F3%2F1024x1024.jpg&h=6432c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww2.hdnux.com/photos/50/64/43/10701005/3/1024x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww2.hdnux.com%2Fphotos%2F5